course.description:
Evaluating
 opportunities and developing a business concept; analyzing new
ventures; pricing, selling, and cost control; attracting stakeholders
and bootstrap finance; the legal form of business and taxation;
financing, deal structure and venture capital; harvesting value;
developing a business plan.

